cast.overview: 70-year-old widower Ben Whittaker has discovered that retirement isn't all it's cracked up to be. Seizing an opportunity to get back in the game, he becomes a senior intern at an online fashion site, founded and run by Jules Ostin.
cast.title: The Intern

details.biography:
G. Keith Alexander is an actor, voiceover artist, and accomplished radio disc jockey. He's been in movies, on TV, and on your radio since the 1970s.

He studied at Fordham University and is the current Founder and CEO of HarlemAmerica Digital Network.
details.name: G. Keith Alexander
